## Cleaning / transformation
```{r}
Exception_data <- read.csv(file = 'Sep-Nov.22.csv')
dfn <- Exception_data[!duplicated(Exception_data[c("MIC_Desc","Result","PostingDate")]),] #drop duplicate attributes
dfn <- dplyr::filter(dfn, MIC_Desc!="Box ID Check")
dfn <- dplyr::filter(dfn, MIC_Desc!="Bag ID Check")

dfn_attribute <- dplyr::filter(dfn, Result=="Reject") #filter by attribute datatype
dfn_variable <- dplyr::filter(dfn, Result !="Reject") #filter by variable datatype
dfn_variable$'Result' <- as.numeric(dfn_variable$'Result')
dfn_variable$'Target' <- as.numeric(dfn_variable$'Target')
dfn
```
